title: Thousands demonstrate in Pamplona against Spanish gang rape case verdict
text:
Thousands demonstrate in Pamplona against Spanish gang rape case verdict Sunday, April 29, 2018 - 00:47
Thousands took to the streets in the Spanish city of Pamplona on Saturday (April 28) to protest against a ruling that cleared five men of the gang rape of a teenager. Rough cut - no reporter narration. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
